e/955c7b3b8e28d5106181e.jpg?width=600&amp;height=739\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/955c7b3b8e28d5106181e.jpg?width=600&amp;height=739\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/955c7b3b8e28d5106181e.jpg?width=600&amp;height=739\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n现在国内的形势如此严峻吗？都不让人好好说话了吗？\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
